# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Firebase — keep project-specific config & secrets out of version control.
# Generate these locally with `flutterfire configure` / the Firebase console.
# (firebase_options.dart is committed as a placeholder; flutterfire overwrites
#  it locally — be careful not to commit real values back unless intended.)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.firebaserc
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
firebase-debug.log
firebase-debug.*.log
.runtimeconfig.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
